window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Best-selling author, superstar physicist, and cofounder of the World Science Festival Brian Greene (<i>The Elegant Universe</i>, <i>The Fabric of the Cosmos</i>) and an ensemble cast led by award-winning actor Paul Rudd (<i>Ant-Man</i>) perform this dramatic story tracing Albert Einstein's discovery of the general theory of relativity. Featuring an original score by composer Jeff Beal (<i>House of Cards</i>, <i>Pollock</i>), Einsteinâ€™s electrifying journey toward his greatest achievement is brought vividly to life. </p> <p>The theatrical version of <i>Light Falls</i> was first performed at the World Science Festival in New York City. </p><p>Full list of narrators includes Graeme Malcolm. </p><p></p>"; 
